data.description: This stunning 2021 build is a perfect blend of modern elegance and technological convenience. Situated in a vibrant neighborhood, this home offers an incredible opportunity with a 2.99% assumable interest rate! Step inside and be captivated by the spacious 1,823 sqft layout that encompasses four bedrooms and two bathrooms. The interior boasts upgraded lighting, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout. This Energy Star House is not only economical but also environmentally conscious, ensuring a sustainable and efficient living space. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, featuring new appliances and updated USB outlets on the kitchen island and countertops. Stay connected and charge your devices effortlessly while enjoying the heart of the home. Every room is designed with your comfort in mind, showcasing ceiling fans to keep you cool and comfortable year-round. The smart home technology adds a layer of convenience, allowing you to control various aspects of your home with just a touch. Exterior cameras provide an added layer of security, allowing you to monitor your property at all times. The ADT security system further enhances peace of mind, ensuring your home is protected around the clock. This meticulously crafted home is not just a place to live; it's a lifestyle upgrade. With its modern amenities, energy efficiency, and security features, it's a haven where you can truly enjoy the comforts of contemporary living.
